/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:1:# Canonical Winning Chain - Criterion-First Geometric Mechanism Stress Test With Theorem-Floor and Same-Currency Gates
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:2:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:3:## Central Premise
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:4:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:5:Geometry is not presumed to be the leading route. It is a hypothesis under audit. This branch is live only if one explicit geometry-aware package and one geometric observable can be defined directly on the suitable-weak / LEI theorem floor, or else on one proxy class whose descent back to that floor is quantitatively cheaper than the target theorem, and if that package-observable pair produces theorem-facing leverage beyond the closest live geometric prior art with all bridge costs, localization costs, and persistence costs paid in the same endpoint currency as the claimed gain.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:6:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:7:If that cannot be shown, the correct output is a bounded obstruction memo or a hybrid geometry-transport handoff, not a rescued geometry narrative.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md:8:
