+# Exploration 002 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Freeze exactly one admissibility decision and one primary comparator for step-015, then judge whether the bridge burden or prior-art overlap already forces a pre-package negative verdict.
+
+## Method
+
+- Build the report from the required local context first.
+- Record verified facts, then explicit inferences, then any scoped proposals.
+- Note dead ends or failed screens if they matter to the verdict.
+
+## Findings Log
+
+### Initial setup
+
+- Report skeleton created.
+
+## Provisional Status
+
+- Outcome: in progress.
+
+## Dead Ends / Failed Attempts
+
+- None yet.
+
+## Open Questions
+
+- Whether the live route is directly suitable-weak / LEI admissible on the theorem floor or only via a named proxy class.
+- Which single geometric prior-art comparator is the closest honest match.
+- Whether admissibility or comparator screening already kills the route before package selection.

